abstract: Japanese figure skater Yuzuru Hanyu leads after men's short program at world championships in Shanghai; other results noted.
lead_paragraph: Hanyu overcame a tumble on his opening quadruple toe loop to take the lead after the men’s short program at the world championships in Shanghai.

headline.main: Yuzuru Hanyu Leads Despite a Fall
